   "body" : "Fixes #11777. Closes #13485.\r\n\r\nWhen calling RPC `stop`, there is a race when the event loop terminates before `HTTPRequest::WriteReply` and so the reply event fails to process. This happens because `event_base_dispatch` returns when there are no active or pending events, which is the case between `InterruptHTTPServer` and `HTTPRequest::WriteReply`.",
